data.description: This updated 2 BR, 3 bath home in Soudan is located minutes from Lake Vermilion!  Home features hard wood flooring throughout, spacious kitchen w/breakfast nook, large dining room and living room and full bath w/whirlpool tub and covered porch on main level.  Upper level includes primary bedroom w/ attached 1/2 bath and 2nd bedroom.  Full lower level includes an area that can be rec room, utility area, 3/4 bath w/tile shower and an additional storage room.  Upgrades of the home include almost new LP gas forced air furnace w/central air, gas hot water heater, 200 amp electric, vinyl siding, windows and roof. Partially fenced back yard, storage shed and 1 stall detached garage.
